            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大埔兩車相撞  私家車陷火海",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"私家車被撞後起火。網圖\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/398fb8ff8ccb622c5918da0d22203694/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250321/_2025032114380649619.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">私家車被撞後起火。網圖</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（21日）午2時許，一輛私家車沿大埔太和路行駛，馳至太湖花園一期對開時，與一輛貨車相撞，私家車車頭起火，司機棄車逃生，幸有驚無險，事件中無人受傷。消防到場將火撲熄，受事故影響，現場交通擠塞。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150567/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"私家車被撞後起火。網圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d17fb764020c258104d9e81ffa184003/2025-03/01_12.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        私家車被撞後起火。網圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150568/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"私家車被撞後起火。網圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/505fc8c0a25141525931d356e148f045/2025-03/02_11.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        私家車被撞後起火。網圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150569/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"私家車被撞後起火。網圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/40355029cbab75757d4f403d9eecd89f/2025-03/03_0_12.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        私家車被撞後起火。網圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150570/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防將火救熄。網圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ac7db181022d4033803355ca22495ea6/2025-03/04_33.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防將火救熄。網圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
