        {
            "title": "警打擊元朗偷車及車內盜竊 拘20男女涉34宗案 起回10部失車",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警打擊元朗偷車及車內盜竊 拘20男女涉34宗案 起回10部失車\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6b2255de33ea60541be81733591b9043/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250321/_2025032114074910288.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警打擊元朗偷車及車內盜竊 拘20男女涉34宗案 起回10部失車</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>近數月元朗警區的車輛盜竊相關案件，包括偷車及車內盜竊等均有上升趨勢。而當中過半數失車更涉及電單車。警方於今年2月7日至3月20日展開代號「星網」的執法行動，成功拘捕19男1女，年齡介乎18至49歲，涉及34宗車輛盜竊相關案件，其中有17部是失車，行動中起回10部。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150510/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方檢獲的偷車工具。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/479f3676fcca610918befbb7bc08168d/2025-03/6ea5c912-48d1-4ea5-af63-01d91d1fb591.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方檢獲的偷車工具。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150511/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方展示檢獲的證物。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8f4d345d5aae4c9c100e2a8d78a84084/2025-03/81b2d505-94db-4347-a74a-bb8e85c5094e.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方展示檢獲的證物。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150512/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"犯案工具。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e3ba4dfdba5b09143802bb3c5b5ae682/2025-03/5152066c-375a-405a-8ebf-5d0136ce12cc.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        犯案工具。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150513/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方展示檢獲的偷車工具。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/52feaacdbf1679632bfd94fe5ae7d611/2025-03/85216530-ef67-45f4-95d3-b4a0353b35c2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方展示檢獲的偷車工具。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150514/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方展示案中證物。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c76e149571673434972d002a9ece31ed/2025-03/b3ae17f6-0003-4c95-b616-87fd2ac7dce4.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方展示案中證物。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150515/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方元朗警區重案組高級督察吳斯軒講述案情。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0868e65cbecbbe8cc327534385a3ee70/2025-03/bf50b9d5-b1b5-4a1d-a563-39263e8ddac5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方元朗警區重案組高級督察吳斯軒講述案情。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>警方元朗警區重案組高級督察吳斯軒講述案情時表示，被捕的20名本地人士，包括19男1女，牽涉元朗區內34宗車輛盜竊相關案件，包括偷車、未獲授權而取用運輸工具，以及車內盜竊。而案件都在凌晨時分發生，在沒有閉路電視覆蓋的露天停泊處或路邊。\n\n</p>\n<p>其中7名被捕人士屬於一個活躍於元朗及天水圍的電單車盜竊團伙。涉案的17部失車，在今次行動中成功起回10部。警方亦都在被捕人的住所內搜獲偷車工具。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方提醒市民，賊人取易不取難，如果要避免成為賊人目標，要時刻保持警覺，駕駛私家車人士離開車輛後要確保門窗已經鎖好，任何情況下勿將車匙及貴重物品放在車內及要鎖門。市民應該避免停泊在僻靜地方，最好選擇有閉路電視覆蓋及有保安的地方，以及安裝防盜裝置及GPS追蹤器。警方重申，偷車屬嚴重罪行，根據香港法例210章盜竊罪條例，一經定罪，最高刑罰監禁10年。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059476/即時-港聞-警打擊元朗偷車及車內盜竊-拘20男女涉34宗案-起回10部失車",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-21 14:21:20",
